{"tid":448037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【新風氣】沙地新王儲走開明路綫 倡「溫和伊斯蘭」","createTime":"2017-10-26T00:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T08:27:53.000Z","uid":73262,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6d039f042f86a8ba67a90175060ee2f2eb602a82","tid":448037,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T00:31:50.000Z","msg":"沙地阿拉伯王儲穆罕默德（Mohammad bin Salman）周二在利雅得的「未來投資倡議」會議上致辭，揚言讓沙地重返昔日「溫和伊斯蘭國家」模樣，對所有宗教和世界持開放態度，又指沙地要在打擊極端主義上加把勁，「我們不會花30年時間去對付極端主義思想，今日就要摧毀它們」。<br />\n<br />\n沙地阿拉伯是君主制國家，由伊斯蘭教遜尼派「瓦哈比主義」（Wahhabism）教徒主導，嚴格奉行瓦哈比主義的清教徒式生活教條，而阿蓋德、「伊斯蘭國」（IS）等恐怖組織發動聖戰的主張，正是來自極端瓦哈比派，因此沙地經常被指贊助恐怖組織。<br />\n<br />\n32歲的穆罕默德年初獲父王薩勒曼擢升為王儲，此前提出社會及經濟改革計劃「2030願景」，被視為沙地政府的改革派，上月更為女性駕駛解禁，但外界認為強硬派教士仍對沙地有強大影響力，質疑他能否扭轉這局面。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171025/57377083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171025%2F57377083&d=rX2kqkPzwmY%2B2aiJgY6s93adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=3610c8d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171025%2F57377083&h=b5300a1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171025/57377083</a>"},{"pid":"0bf2789bef93fddb9ff12b6316e1ee520ee5c4c6","tid":448037,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T00:33:31.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"9b5e1f8784b0af35e4dad8c8370580dc0a0aaab7","tid":448037,"uid":12575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T00:36:39.000Z","msg":"有錢成咁 仲同你走乜嘢isis路線咩"},{"pid":"0f4a99213b44686029eaae4b69b8c0a22b50c47f","tid":448037,"uid":53223,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T00:39:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢成咁 仲同你走乜嘢isis路線咩</blockquote><br />\n沙特係成功左的Isis"},{"pid":"8cf6a6bade6f58e84fdfa8d2647e11a04daaba8b","tid":448037,"uid":60766,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":